# Recommended software

This is a list of good software, containing standalone programs &amp; libraries.
Good software meaning it aligns with at least a part of our minimalistic mindset.
All entries are alphabetically sorted by their name.

name            source                                      desc

chibicc         <https://github.com/rui314/chibicc>         Small C compiler
dwm             <https://dwm.suckless.org>                  Window manager by suckless
fzf             <https://github.com/junegunn/fzf>           Command line fuzzy finder
ripgrep         <https://github.com/BurntSushi/ripgrep>     Fast grep + fzf integration
st              <https://st.suckless.org>                   Simple terminal implementation for X
utf.8           <https://github.com/sheredom/utf8.h>        UTF-8 string library
